From: Tzachi Shaiovitch <tzachish1@gmail.com>
Date: Wed, 21 Jan 2026 10:08:33 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 03/22] feat(editor): Add node governance integration to node
 picker

- Add NodeGovernanceStatus interface to SimplifiedNodeType
- Modify NodeItem.vue to display blocked/pending status
- Add lock icon and 'Request access' link for blocked nodes
- Create NodeAccessRequestModal for users to request access
- Add governance constants and register modal globally
- Add i18n strings for blocked state and access request modal
- Implement visual feedback for governance state in node creator
